    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305060/extras/508de13743e3f666c7e232752385289b.poster.avif?t=1761321623\" width=600 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305060/extras/508de13743e3f666c7e232752385289b.webm?t=1761321623\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305060/extras/508de13743e3f666c7e232752385289b.mp4?t=1761321623\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to <strong>Escape Floor 13</strong>, a tense, atmospheric survival puzzle game where every step could be your last. You find yourself trapped on the mysterious 13th floor of a hotel, and the only way out is down. To reach safety, you must navigate each floor carefully, but beware—supernatural anomalies haunt these hallways.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305060/extras/60b8e240ebd818a7c253c14938942a58.poster.avif?t=1761321623\" width=600 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305060/extras/60b8e240ebd818a7c253c14938942a58.webm?t=1761321623\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305060/extras/60b8e240ebd818a7c253c14938942a58.mp4?t=1761321623\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The goal is simple: cross each floor and reach the elevator on the other side. But if you sense an anomaly, you must retreat to the elevator you came from. Will you survive the journey to freedom, or will the 13th floor become your final stop?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305060/extras/e5b0aa9c21baafacdb6948790a981ea3.poster.avif?t=1761321623\" width=600 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305060/extras/e5b0aa9c21baafacdb6948790a981ea3.webm?t=1761321623\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305060/extras/e5b0aa9c21baafacdb6948790a981ea3.mp4?t=1761321623\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The hotel is always watching. Stay alert, trust your instincts, and escape… before it’s too late.</p>",
